the dead girls uncle vincenzo giorgi 25 is being held for 
questioning by police in connection with the murder of her surgeon 
locri hospital proclaimed a day of silence tuesday to protest 
the killing of dr gino marino who operated on the girl friday 
marino died early sunday of gunshot wounds to the head his 
killers ambushed his car saturday night shooting out a tire to stop 
it and then shooting marino police said 
various operating wards at hospitals throughout the southern 
region of calabria also closed tuesday to protest the lack of police 
protection for doctors according to news reports 
