<TEXT>
the defense department bracing for charges of 
censorship at the stars amp stripes military newspapers is debating a 
significant shift in structure that would put civilian journalists 
at the top of the masthead instead of military officers 
pentagon officials say no final decision has been made to ditch 
the existing organizational system but the officials say there 
