must be careful with meat prices because we burned ourselves a few 
times with it thats not the way the market should decide how much 
ham costs 
under rationing each person gets 5 pounds of meat a month 
except manual laborers such as miners and steelworkers who receive 
nearly 10 pounds meat also can be bought without ration cards at 
private meat shops where the price is about three to four times as 
much as meat bought with the cards 
