the suit against fogerty and his current recording company 
warner bros records inc contends old man down the road a 
single from fogertys solo centerfield album copied the melody 
from run through the jungle which fogerty wrote and sang for 
creedence in 1970 and to which fantasy now owns the rights 
relations between fogerty and his former recording company have 
