computer sound system that superimposed one pattern of notes on 
another 
a defense musicologist for warner bros guided the us district 
court jurors through a series of creedence records green 
river keep on chooglin tombstone shadow and bootleg 
with his own series of elaborate charts pointing out similarities 
to run through the jungle and old man down the road 
