for cadets at the great lakes maritime academy such training in 
current navigational technology is combined with the guidance of 
experienced sailors 
its much better training than you can get on a ship because we 
can simulate nearcollisions or running aground said rear adm 
james f mcnulty superintendent of the academy which is part of 
