current office governor of massachusetts 
personal dukakis was born nov 3 1933 in brookline mass his 
parents panos dukakis and euterpe boukis dukakis greek immigrants 
michael dukakis and his wife the former katharine dickson have 
three children john andrea and kara 
education dukakis received a bachelors degree in political 
