companys industry record of 166 billion in earnings in the second 
quarter typically thirdquarter earnings are lower than other 
quarters for automakers because of factory retooling to gear up for 
the new model year which traditionally begins oct 1 
the ford teams successful effort worldwide to provide products 
with improved quality and good customer value again is evident in 
our thirdquarter results ford chairman donald petersen and vice 
